            <title>[HADOOP-18363] Fix bug preventing hadoop-metrics2 from emitting metrics to &gt; 1 Ganglia servers.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-18363</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AbstractGangliaSink is used by the hadoop-metrics2 package to emit metrics to Ganglia. Currently, this class uses the apache commons-configuration package to read from the hadoop-metrics2.properties file. commons-configuration is outdated, and has a bug where the .getString function drops everything after the first comma.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
